{"Id":212,"LanguageCodes":["ja","jpn"],"Name":"jpn-ryoichimita","Author":"Ryoichi Mita","Language":"Japanese","Description":"Japanese","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/japanese_meta/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/japanese_meta , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"恐れ戦く日（最後の審判）"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"恐れ戦く日とは何か。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"恐れ戦く日が，何であるかをあなたに理解させるものは何か。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"（それは）人間が飛散する蛾のようになる日。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"また山々が，梳かれた羊毛のようになる（日である）。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"それで，かれの秤が（善行で）重い者は，"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"幸福で満ち足りて暮らすであろう。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"だが秤の軽い者は，"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"奈落が，かれの里であろう。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"それが何であるかを，あなたに理解させるものは何か。"},{"SurahNumber":101,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"（それは）焦熱（地獄）の火。"}]}